name: Något sover under Aitik
description:
Control your Norrlänning with the arrow keys. Use space to place bombs once you bought them. Progress is saved in localstorage so you can continue with the same inventory next time you start the game.

To reset progress (or to cheat :p) removed/edit the localstorage key "spelsylt5-inventory".
Spent ~3 h / day.
Music made in Ableton. Uses a wind sfx from http://soundbible.com/1810-Wind.html.
